react ke ander addeventlistener ka alternative --> onClick={} se hum event handling krte hi.
    props addition kke dvara hum event handling krte hi.
    addeventlistener ek imperative approach.

 UI ko change krna value ke change hone pr.
    'kabhi koi bhi cheez change krne par use dikhana ho to hum use state concept.. 

    value change krne se UI change nhi hoga , without state concept.

    import {userState} from 'react'
    const [tittle , setTittle] = userState(props.tittle);
    // user state do cheeze return krta hi , first the value , current wali , and and a function to set it
    so for changes at UI
        first change first output of userState , then use setter means the 2nd function.

Syntax ka ratta nhi marna krte krte khud hi yaad ho jayega nhi to net pr dekh loonga.

