onchange() , event ko input  field ke ander lagaya to kya hua, ye bhi  onclick event ki tarah hi hi.
    isse jaise hi hhum input ke ander kuch likhenge , wo turant hi hander ko call kr dega
    onchange(handler) , as a input property ,  

    isme hander ke ander event naam ka object by default aata hi
    so event.target.value ka use krke hum uske ander ki value dekh sakte hi. 

event --> addevent listener ke ander hum jis cheez ke upar bhi listener laga rhe hote hi , usko hum event ke dvara fetch kr sakte hi 

setTittle , setDate ye saare function , saare function , scedule kr dete hi.

userstate ke jariye hi hum kayi sare parameters bhi change kr sakte hi

objet bna ke sab ko ek saath bhi kr sakte hi. 

